285
00:29:49,575 --> 00:29:51,325
noquear...

286
00:29:51,492 --> 00:29:53,200
digamos, una vaca?

287
00:29:54,825 --> 00:29:57,950
Solo por... siete u ocho horas.

288
00:29:58,117 --> 00:29:59,700
Para que...

289
00:30:01,534 --> 00:30:04,867
